      <h1>‘We are living in perpetual fear’: Prajwal Revanna video leaks spark panic among women in Hassan</h1>
      <h2>Activists in the Karnakata city contend that the police should have acted earlier to protect the women and arrest the MP.</h2>
      <!-- MOBILE & TABLET ONLY META-->
